"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.2.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.2.4</span> 標題：門柱（doorpost）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אַמָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’amah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:4\">ISA 6:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֹמְנָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’omnah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:16\">2KI 18:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מְזוּזָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mzuzah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:7\">EXO 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22\">EXO 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:23\">EXO 12:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:6\">EXO 21:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:9\">DEU 6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:20\">DEU 11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:3\">JDG 16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:9\">1SA 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:31\">1KI 6:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:33\">1KI 6:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:5\">1KI 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:34\">PRO 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:8\">ISA 57:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:21\">EZK 41:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:8\">EZK 43:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:8\">EZK 43:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:19\">EZK 45:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:19\">EZK 45:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:2\">EZK 46:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： סַף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： saf)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:7</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0029_doorpost_lintel_hant.png\" alt=\"OAI-0029_doorpost_lintel_hant\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>房門和大門這類入口為長方形。門口的兩側有時會襯上木頭，這樣門的合頁就可以固定在木頭上。門柱就是門口兩側的這些柱子。門柱還可支撐門口上方的結構。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果目標語言沒有表示門框各個部分的專業詞語，翻譯者可以使用描述性短語，例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:22\">EXO 12:22</a> 可譯為「門楣和兩根門柱」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 直譯），或「門框的兩側和頂部」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:16\">2KI 18:16</a> ：希伯來文<em>’omnah</em> 在整本聖經中只出現在這一處，意思不確定。其動詞詞根的意思是「攜帶、支撐」，既可以指一個大房間中的支柱，也可以指支撐門口的柱子。大多數譯本都採用第二種解釋，譯為「門柱」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
